{"type":"message","id":"114b968b","parentId":"cad9c9e2","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:34:03.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#Requires -Version 5.1\n#Requires -RunAsAdministrator\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    小豆芽自动化控制模块 - PowerShell函数库\n.DESCRIPTION\n    提供进程管理、窗口控制、UI自动化等功能，用于控制小豆芽应用\n.NOTES\n    作者: OpenClaw\n    版本: 1.0\n    编码: UTF-8 BOM\n#>\n\n# =============================================================================\n# 配置常量\n# =============================================================================\n$script:XiaodouyaPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\xiaodouya\\新版小豆芽.exe\"\n$script:XiaodouyaProcessName = \"新版小豆芽\"\n$script:LogEnabled = $true\n$script:LogPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\xiaodouya_automation.log\"\n\n# =============================================================================\n# 日志函数\n# =============================================================================\nfunction Write-XiaodouyaLog {\n    param(\n        [string]$Message,\n        [ValidateSet(\"INFO\", \"WARN\", \"ERROR\", \"DEBUG\")]\n        [string]$Level = \"INFO\"\n    )\n    \n    if (-not $script:LogEnabled) { return }\n    \n    $timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    $logEntry = \"[$timestamp] [$Level] $Message\"\n    \n    try {\n        Add-Content -Path $script:LogPath -Value $logEntry -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    } catch {\n        # 静默失败，不影响主功能\n    }\n}\n\n# =============================================================================\n# 进程管理\n# =============================================================================\n\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    查找所有小豆芽进程\n\n[440 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772174043994}}
{"type":"message","id":"08153a20","parentId":"114b968b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:34:34.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前进度：已创建了核心PowerShell函数库的前12766字节，包含日志函数和进程管理函数（Get-XiaodouyaProcess、Start-Xiaodouya、Stop-Xiaodouya）。\n\n需要继续完成剩余内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前进度：\n\n**已完成：**\n- ✅ 核心PowerShell函数库 `xiaodouya_functions.ps1` 框架\n- ✅ 日志系统 (`Write-XiaodouyaLog`)\n- ✅ 进程管理函数 (Get-XiaodouyaProcess, Start-Xiaodouya, Stop-Xiaodouya)\n- ✅ User32 API声明（用于窗口控制）\n\n**正在进行中：**\n- 窗口控制函数（Get-XiaodouyaWindow, Set-XiaodouyaActive, Move-XiaodouyaWindow等）\n- UI自动化函数\n- 截图和按键功能\n\n**待完成：**\n- WSL2别名脚本 `xiaodouya_aliases.sh`\n- 测试脚本 `test_xiaodouya.sh`\n- README文档 `XIAODOUYA_CONTROLS.md`\n\n继续完成PowerShell函数库..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_functions.ps1","offset":350,"limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":15887,"output":330,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16217,"cost":{"input":0.0000015887000000000001,"output":6.600000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000016547000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772174043999}}
{"type":"message","id":"b000f409","parentId":"08153a20","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:34:34.575Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        }\n        \n        $result = [User32]::ShowWindow($window.Handle, [User32]::SW_MINIMIZE)\n        \n        if ($result) {\n            Write-Host \"小豆芽窗口已最小化\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-XiaodouyaLog \"窗口最小化成功\" -Level \"INFO\"\n        }\n        \n        return $result\n    }\n    catch {\n        Write-Error \"最小化窗口失败: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n        Write-XiaodouyaLog \"最小化失败: $($_.Exception.Message)\" -Level \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    最大化小豆芽窗口\n.DESCRIPTION\n    将小豆芽窗口最大化\n#>\nfunction Set-XiaodouyaMaximize {\n    [CmdletBinding()]\n    param()\n    \n    Write-XiaodouyaLog \"最大化窗口...\" -Level \"INFO\"\n    \n    try {\n        $window = Get-XiaodouyaWindow\n        if (-not $window) {\n            Write-Error \"无法获取窗口\"\n            return $false\n        }\n        \n        $result = [User32]::ShowWindow($window.Handle, [User32]::SW_MAXIMIZE)\n        \n        if ($result) {\n            Write-Host \"小豆芽窗口已最大化\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-XiaodouyaLog \"窗口最大化成功\" -Level \"INFO\"\n        }\n        \n        return $result\n    }\n    catch {\n        Write-Error \"最大化窗口失败: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n        Write-XiaodouyaLog \"最大化失败: $($_.Exception.Message)\" -Level \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    移动小豆芽窗口\n.DESCRIPTION\n    将小豆芽窗口移动到指定位置\n.PARAMETER X\n    新的X坐标\n.PARAMETER Y\n    新的Y坐标\n.PARAMETER Width\n    新的宽度（可选）\n.PARAMETER Height\n    新的高度（可选）\n#>\nfunction Move-XiaodouyaWindow {\n    [CmdletBinding()]\n    param(\n        [Parameter(Mandatory = $true)]\n        [int]$X,\n        \n        [Parameter(Mandatory = $true)]\n        [int]$Y,\n        \n        [int]$Width = 0,\n        [int]$Height = 0\n    )\n    \n    Write-XiaodouyaLog \"移动窗口到 ($X, $Y)...\" -Level \"INFO\"\n    \n    try {\n        $window = Get-XiaodouyaWindow\n        if (-not $window) {\n            Write-Error \"无法获取窗口\"\n            return $false\n        }\n        \n        # 如果没有指定宽高，使用当前宽高\n        if ($Width -eq 0) { $Width = $window.Width }\n        if ($Height -eq 0) { $Height = $window.Height }\n        \n        $result = [User32]::MoveWindow($window.Handle, $X, $Y, $Width, $Height, $true)\n        \n        if ($result) {\n            Write-Host \"窗口已移动到 ($X, $Y)，大小 ${Width}x${Height}\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-XiaodouyaLog \"窗口移动成功\" -Level \"INFO\"\n        }\n        \n\n[41 more lines in file. Use offset=450 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772174074571}}
