{"type":"message","id":"2930d2ba","parentId":"c52cb403","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:45:02.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建完整的别名脚本和文档：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:11","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_aliases.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# =============================================================================\n# 小豆芽 PowerShell 别名脚本\n# 用于从 WSL2 快速控制 Windows 上的小豆芽应用\n# \n# 使用方法:\n#   source xiaodouya_aliases.sh    # 加载别名\n#   xdy-help                       # 显示帮助\n# =============================================================================\n\n# PowerShell 路径\nPOWERSHELL=\"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/v1.0/powershell.exe\"\nPS_CMD=\"$POWERSHELL -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command\"\n\n# 加载PowerShell模块的路径\nPS_PROFILE_PATH=\"$USERPROFILE/Documents/WindowsPowerShell/Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 核心别名 - 进程管理\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# 查找小豆芽进程\nalias xdy-find='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Get-XiaodouyaProcess | Format-Table Id, ProcessName, MainWindowTitle -AutoSize\"'\n\n# 启动小豆芽\nalias xdy-start='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Start-Xiaodouya -Wait; Start-Sleep 1\"'\n\n# 停止小豆芽\nalias xdy-stop='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Stop-Xiaodouya -Force\"'\n\n# 重启小豆芽\nalias xdy-restart='xdy-stop && sleep 2 && xdy-start'\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 窗口控制别名\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# 激活窗口到前台\nalias xdy-active='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Set-XiaodouyaActive\"'\n\n# 最小化窗口\nalias xdy-min='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Set-XiaodouyaMinimize\"'\n\n# 最大化窗口\nalias xdy-max='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Set-XiaodouyaMaximize\"'\n\n# 获取窗口信息\nalias xdy-info='$PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Get-XiaodouyaWindow | Format-List\"'\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 位置和移动别名\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# 移动窗口到指定位置\n# 用法: xdy-move 100 200\nxdy-move() {\n    if [ $# -lt 2 ]; then\n        echo \"用法: xdy-move <X> <Y> [宽度] [高度]\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    local X=\"$1\"\n    local Y=\"$2\"\n    local W=\"${3:-0}\"\n    local H=\"${4:-0}\"\n    $PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Move-XiaodouyaWindow -X $X -Y $Y -Width $W -Height $H\"\n}\n\n# 居中窗口\nxdy-center() {\n    $PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} \n        Add-Type @\\\"`nusing System;`nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;`npublic class User32 {`n    [DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")] public static extern bool GetWindowRect(IntPtr hWnd, out RECT lpRect);`n    [DllImport(\\\"user32.dll\\\")] public static extern bool MoveWindow(IntPtr hWnd, int X, int Y, int nWidth, int nHeight, bool bRepaint);`n    public struct RECT { public int Left; public int Top; public int Right; public int Bottom; }`n}`n\\\";`n`$proc = Get-Process | Where-Object { `$_.MainWindowTitle -like \\\"*小豆芽*\\\" } | Select-Object -First 1;`nif (`$proc) {`n    `$screen = [System.Windows.Forms.Screen]::PrimaryScreen.WorkingArea;`n    `$rect = New-Object User32+RECT;`n    [User32]::GetWindowRect(`$proc.MainWindowHandle, [ref]`$rect);`n    `$w = `$rect.Right - `$rect.Left;`n    `$h = `$rect.Bottom - `$rect.Top;`n    `$x = [int]((`$screen.Width - `$w) / 2);`n    `$y = [int]((`$screen.Height - `$h) / 2);`n    [User32]::MoveWindow(`$proc.MainWindowHandle, `$x, `$y, `$w, `$h, `$true);`n    Write-Host \\\"窗口已居中\\\";`n}\"\n}\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 截图和高级功能\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# 截图\n# 用法: xdy-screenshot [保存路径]\nxdy-screenshot() {\n    local path=\"${1:-$USERPROFILE/Documents/xiaodouya_screenshot_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).png}\"\n    # 转换路径为Windows格式\n    local winpath=$(echo \"$path\" | sed 's|^/mnt/c/|C:\\\\|g; s|/|\\\\|g')\n    $PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} New-XiaodouyaScreenshot -Path '$winpath'\"\n}\n\n# 发送按键\n# 用法: xdy-keys \"按键序列\"\nxdy-keys() {\n    if [ $# -lt 1 ]; then\n        echo \"用法: xdy-keys \\\"按键序列\\\"\"\n        echo \"示例: xdy-keys \\\"{ENTER}\\\"    - 按回车\"\n        echo \"       xdy-keys \\\"{TAB}\\\"      - 按Tab\"\n        echo \"       xdy-keys \\\"hello\\\"     - 输入文本\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    local keys=\"$1\"\n    $PS_CMD \"& {$PS_PROFILE_PATH} Send-XiaodouyaKeys -Keys '$keys'\"\n}\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 实用别名\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# 重新加载别名\nalias xdy-reload='source ~/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_aliases.sh'\n\n# 显示帮助\nalias xdy-help='\necho \"===========================================\"\necho \"   小豆芽 PowerShell 命令别名\"\necho \"===========================================\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【进程管理】\"\necho \"  xdy-find      - 查找小豆芽进程\"\necho \"  xdy-start     - 启动小豆芽\"\necho \"  xdy-stop      - 停止小豆芽\"\necho \"  xdy-restart   - 重启小豆芽\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【窗口控制】\"\necho \"  xdy-active    - 激活窗口到前台\"\necho \"  xdy-min       - 最小化窗口\"\necho \"  xdy-max       - 最大化窗口\"\necho \"  xdy-info      - 显示窗口信息\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【位置控制】\"\necho \"  xdy-move X Y [W H]  - 移动窗口\"\necho \"  xdy-center          - 窗口居中\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【高级功能】\"\necho \"  xdy-screenshot [path] - 截图\"\necho \"  xdy-keys \\\"keys\\\"       - 发送按键\"\necho \"\"\necho \"【其他】\"\necho \"  xdy-help      - 显示此帮助\"\necho \"  xdy-reload    - 重新加载别名\"\necho \"===========================================\"\n'\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 初始化提示\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\necho \"小豆芽控制别名已加载。输入 xdy-help 查看可用命令。\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:12","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/test_xiaodouya.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# =============================================================================\n# 小豆芽 PowerShell 模块测试脚本\n# 功能: 测试所有核心功能的完整工作流程\n# =============================================================================\n\nset -e  # 遇到错误立即退出\n\n# 颜色定义\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m' # No Color\n\n# 测试计数器\nTESTS_PASSED=0\nTESTS_FAILED=0\n\n# 打印函数\nprint_header() {\n    echo \"\"\n    echo -e \"${BLUE}=========================================${NC}\"\n    echo -e \"${BLUE}  $1${NC}\"\n    echo -e \"${BLUE}=========================================${NC}\"\n}\n\nprint_success() {\n    echo -e \"${GREEN}✓ $1${NC}\"\n    ((TESTS_PASSED++))\n}\n\nprint_error() {\n    echo -e \"${RED}✗ $1${NC}\"\n    ((TESTS_FAILED++))\n}\n\nprint_info() {\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}ℹ $1${NC}\"\n}\n\n# 检查命令是否可用\ncheck_command() {\n    if command -v \"$1\" &> /dev/null; then\n        return 0\n    else\n        return 1\n    fi\n}\n\n# 等待用户确认\nwait_for_confirm() {\n    echo \"\"\n    read -p \"按 Enter 继续...\"\n}\n\n# =============================================================================\n# 测试套件\n# =============================================================================\n\nprint_header \"小豆芽 PowerShell 模块测试\"\nprint_info \"测试环境: WSL2 -> Windows PowerShell\"\necho \"\"\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 前置检查\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"前置检查\"\n\nif check_command powershell.exe; then\n    print_success \"PowerShell 可访问\"\nelse\n    print_error \"无法访问 PowerShell\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 检查别名文件\nif [ -f \"$(dirname \"$0\")/xiaodouya_aliases.sh\" ]; then\n    print_success \"别名脚本存在\"\nelse\n    print_error \"找不到别名脚本\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 加载别名\nsource \"$(dirname \"$0\")/xiaodouya_aliases.sh\"\nprint_success \"别名脚本已加载\"\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 1: 查找进程\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 1: 查找进程\"\nprint_info \"正在查找小豆芽进程...\"\n\nif xdy-find > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"进程查找功能正常\"\nelse\n    print_error \"进程查找失败\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 2: 窗口信息\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 2: 获取窗口信息\"\nprint_info \"正在获取窗口信息...\"\n\nif xdy-info > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"窗口信息获取成功\"\n    xdy-info 2>/dev/null | head -20\nelse\n    print_error \"无法获取窗口信息（小豆芽可能未运行）\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 3: 窗口控制\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 3: 窗口控制\"\n\n# 测试最小化\nprint_info \"测试最小化...\"\nif xdy-min > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"最小化命令执行成功\"\n    sleep 1\n    \n    # 恢复窗口\n    print_info \"恢复窗口...\"\n    xdy-active > /dev/null 2>&1\n    sleep 1\nelse\n    print_error \"最小化失败\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 4: 窗口位置\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 4: 窗口位置控制\"\n\n# 获取当前位置\nprint_info \"获取当前窗口位置...\"\nCURRENT_POS=$(xdy-info 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"Left|Top\" | head -2)\nprint_info \"当前位置: $CURRENT_POS\"\n\n# 移动窗口\nprint_info \"移动窗口到 (100, 100)...\"\nif xdy-move 100 100 > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"移动命令执行成功\"\n    sleep 1\n    \n    # 恢复原位置\n    print_info \"恢复窗口位置...\"\n    xdy-active > /dev/null 2>&1\nelse\n    print_error \"移动窗口失败\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 5: 截图功能\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 5: 截图功能\"\n\nSCREENSHOT_PATH=\"$USERPROFILE/Documents/xiaodouya_test_screenshot.png\"\nprint_info \"正在截图...\"\n\nif xdy-screenshot \"$SCREENSHOT_PATH\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"截图成功保存到: $SCREENSHOT_PATH\"\n    \n    # 检查文件是否存在\n    if [ -f \"/mnt/c${SCREENSHOT_PATH//C:/}\" ] 2>/dev/null || [ -f \"$SCREENSHOT_PATH\" ] 2>/dev/null; then\n        print_success \"截图文件已创建\"\n    else\n        print_error \"截图文件未找到\"\n    fi\nelse\n    print_error \"截图失败\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试 6: 按键发送\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试 6: 按键发送\"\n\nprint_info \"测试发送 Tab 键...\"\nif xdy-keys \"{TAB}\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    print_success \"按键发送成功\"\nelse\n    print_error \"按键发送失败\"\nfi\n\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# 测试结果汇总\n# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nprint_header \"测试结果汇总\"\necho \"\"\necho -e \"${GREEN}通过: $TESTS_PASSED${NC}\"\necho -e \"${RED}失败: $TESTS_FAILED${NC}\"\necho \"\"\n\nTOTAL=$((TESTS_PASSED + TESTS_FAILED))\nif [ $TESTS_FAILED -eq 0 ]; then\n    print_header \"🎉 所有测试通过!\"\n    exit 0\nelse\n    print_header \"⚠️ 部分测试失败\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:13","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/XIAODOUYA_CONTROLS.md","content":"# 小豆芽 PowerShell 控制命令库\n\n一套完整的 PowerShell 函数和 WSL2 bash 别名，用于自动化控制小豆芽应用。\n\n## 📁 文件说明\n\n| 文件 | 位置 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `xiaodouya_functions.ps1` | Windows 文档目录 | PowerShell 核心函数库 |\n| `xiaodouya_aliases.sh` | WSL2 工作目录 | Bash 别名脚本 |\n| `test_xiaodouya.sh` | WSL2 工作目录 | 功能测试脚本 |\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n### 1. 安装 PowerShell 函数库\n\n打开 PowerShell（以管理员身份），执行：\n\n```powershell\n# 创建 PowerShell 配置文件目录（如果不存在）\n$profileDir = Split-Path -Parent $PROFILE\nif (!(Test-Path $profileDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $profileDir -Force\n}\n\n# 复制函数库到配置文件\nCopy-Item \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\xiaodouya_functions.ps1\" $PROFILE -Force\n\n# 重新加载配置\n. $PROFILE\n```\n\n### 2. 加载 WSL2 别名\n\n在 WSL2 终端中执行：\n\n```bash\n# 临时加载（当前会话有效）\nsource ~/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_aliases.sh\n\n# 永久加载（添加到 .bashrc）\necho \"source ~/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_aliases.sh\" >> ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n### 3. 验证安装\n\n```bash\n# 显示帮助\nxdy-help\n\n# 查找小豆芽进程\nxdy-find\n```\n\n## 📚 命令参考\n\n### 进程管理\n\n| 命令 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `xdy-find` | 查找小豆芽进程 | `xdy-find` |\n| `xdy-start` | 启动小豆芽 | `xdy-start` |\n| `xdy-stop` | 停止小豆芽 | `xdy-stop` |\n| `xdy-restart` | 重启小豆芽 | `xdy-restart` |\n\n### 窗口控制\n\n| 命令 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `xdy-active` | 激活窗口到前台 | `xdy-active` |\n| `xdy-min` | 最小化窗口 | `xdy-min` |\n| `xdy-max` | 最大化窗口 | `xdy-max` |\n| `xdy-info` | 显示窗口信息 | `xdy-info` |\n\n### 位置控制\n\n| 命令 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `xdy-move X Y [W H]` | 移动窗口 | `xdy-move 100 200` |\n| `xdy-center` | 窗口居中 | `xdy-center` |\n\n### 高级功能\n\n| 命令 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `xdy-screenshot [path]` | 截图 | `xdy-screenshot` |\n| `xdy-keys \"keys\"` | 发送按键 | `xdy-keys \"{TAB}\"` |\n\n## 🔧 PowerShell 原生使用\n\n如果你更喜欢直接使用 PowerShell，可以：\n\n```powershell\n# 加载模块\nImport-Module \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1\"\n\n# 查看可用函数\nGet-Command -Module XiaodouyaAutomation\n\n# 使用函数\nGet-XiaodouyaProcess\nStart-Xiaodouya\nSet"}},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"-X","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":25601,"output":8192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33793,"cost":{"input":0.0000025601000000000003,"output":0.0000016384,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000041985000000000005}},"stopReason":"length","timestamp":1772174511760}}
